data.title: Taj Burrow in VonZipper Pinch Sunglasses
data.description:
Story: Some say that big things come in small packages. Get a grip and give yourself a Pinch, because this modern classic is too good to be true.

Specs: VonZipper Pinch sunglasses are handmade in Italy; the frame is crafted from nylon grilamid and held together with stainless steel optical hinges. The base 6 spherical impact resistant polycarbonate lenses will protect your eyes with 100% UV protection.

data.title: VonZipper : F.C.G. // Freethinkers Conspiracy Guild 2014
data.description:
The fundamental premise of the Freethinkers Conspiracy Guild is that all people have the right to do everything in their power to achieve the greatest amount of pleasure possible to them. The Guild applauds those who question and challenge national myths, strive to be above the chains of mediocrity and seek the greater forms of life’s indulgences. A Society of individuals, Freethinkers, opinions are formed on the basis of an understanding and rejection of tradition, authority or established belief proposed by the trappings of common acceptance.

The Guild is a challenge to the direction of eyewear and a direct interpretation of the truths found within the “F.C.G.” The effects of authority, conformity, or conventional wisdom of popular culture does not limit the collection. Forward thinking and more contemporary than ordinary, these frames are styled independent of any logical fallacies.

Doubt everything.. Find your own light….

data.title: VonZipper : Hell On Wheels
data.description: A throwback race held in the spirit of "run what you brung," VonZipper pulled out their old dirt bikes and teamed up with the folks at The Hell on Wheels for a weekend of camping, and popping wheelies. Join the VZ FreewheelerMX club over Thanksgiving weekend at Glen Helen Raceway as they eat their leftovers and some dust at the Red Bull Day in the Dirt.
